author: IGN
description:
Take a look at the Kid's Choice Awards Trailer for Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds, an upcoming arcade racing game developed by SEGA. Players can take to the streets of Bikini Bottom to race as SpongeBob SquarePants and Patrick Star. Outpace the competition in iconic locations from the Nickelodeon show, including the Krusty Krab to the Patty Wagon. Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds is launching on September 25 for PlayStation 4 (PS4), PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, Nintendo Switch 2, and PC (Steam and Epic Games Store).

#SonicRacingCrossworlds #Spongebob #Gaming
title: Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds - Official Kid's Choice Awards Trailer

author: IGN
description:
Dying Light: The Beast art director Katarzyna Tarnacka-Polito shows you Castor Woods, the new setting for the latest game in the first-person zombie-hunting melee-plus-parkour action-adventure where you, as Kyle Crane, must wield the powers of The Beast in his quest for revenge. Dying Light: The Beast will be released on August 22 for PC, PS5, and Xbox Series X|S. Wishlist it on Steam if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3008130/Dying_Light_The_Beast


#IGN #Gaming
title: Dying Light: The Beast – Exploring Castor Woods | IGN First

author: IGN
description:
Death Stranding 2: On the Beach is nearly here. And, if you’re like us, you could probably do with a recap of all of the important events of the first game before you jump into the sequel. After all, it wasn’t that simple to wrap your head around the first time, was it? Here we’ll take you through the original game’s story as succinctly as we possibly can, as well as go through what we know about the sequel and where the path could lead for its cast of characters.

#IGN  #Gaming #DeathStranding
title: Death Stranding: The Story So Far
